@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
autonumber

actor "Backoffice Operator" as BackofficeOperator
participant ":System" as System

activate BackofficeOperator

BackofficeOperator -> System : Requests to disable a customer's collaborator

activate System
System --> BackofficeOperator : Requests customer and collaborator identification
deactivate System

BackofficeOperator -> System : Provides customer and collaborator identification

activate System
System --> System : Check if Backoffice Operator is authorized
System --> System : Validate customer
System --> System : Validate collaborator
System --> System : Check if collaborator belongs to customer
System --> System : Check if collaborator is active

alt collaborator can be disabled
    System --> System : Disable collaborator
    System --> System : Disable corresponding system user access
    System --> BackofficeOperator : Collaborator disabled successfully
else collaborator cannot be disabled
    System --> BackofficeOperator : Display error message
end

deactivate System
deactivate BackofficeOperator

@enduml